org.perfcake.message.generator

Class AbstractMessageGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.generator.AbstractMessageGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageGenerator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultMessageGenerator

    public abstract class AbstractMessageGenerator
extends Object
implements MessageGenerator
    A common ancestor for most generators. It can generate messages in parallel using Message Senders running concurrently in threads number of threads.
    Author:
    Pavel Macík, Martin Večeřa
